sources.title: Komodo Vs Cobra | Full Movie | Monster Action Adventure | King Cobra
sources.description:
Komodo vs. Cobra - When a top secret island research facility goes dark, a crack team of commandos is sent to investigate. Once there, they are shocked to find that giant komodo dragons and cobras live on this island and they're really hungry. Now with the deck stacked against them, and nearly no hope for survival, the team is locked in a battle of survival with two of nature's most formidable predators.
2005.  Stars: Michael Paré, Michelle Borth, Ryan McTavish
